♪Holding a sword that pierces nine heavens
I'm as carefree as I can be♪

2
00:00:35,380 --> 00:00:40,980
♪Not going to waste my youth while I'm young♪

3
00:00:41,140 --> 00:00:43,900
♪I slay demons at the end of the divine path♪

4
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:46,860
♪I stop by Hell♪

5
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:52,940
♪I accept all challenges that come my way♪

6
00:00:53,340 --> 00:00:59,020
♪A young man with two lives♪

7
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:04,860
♪Roaming the martial world
hundreds of nations under his feet♪

8
00:01:05,140 --> 00:01:07,900
♪Had his bloodline awakened in a secret realm♪

9
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:11,180
♪Refined his body from the inside
in thunderstorms♪

10
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:16,500
♪A hero of the ancient world♪

11
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:20,060
♪Boiling hot human blood♪

12
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:23,100
♪His hand stretches through space♪

13
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:28,260
♪Which fighter will make it to the top?♪

14
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:34,140
♪In the 33rd realm
he'll be slashing the great sky♪

15
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:37,540
♪That's me, a living legend♪

16
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:41,900
[Dominator of Martial Gods]

17
00:01:42,180 --> 00:01:45,980
[Adapted from original work of "Dominator of Martial Gods",
The Universe Part I by Ruo Hong Culture]

18
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:49,220
[Episode 20]

19
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:55,710
[The Mount of Demonic Ancestors]

20
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:56,950
The Mount of Demonic Ancestors

21
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:59,480
is full of danger,
with many blood beasts living in it.

22
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,590
And Bloodmist Holy Land

23
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:04,000
is in the depths of the Mountain.

24
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,430
With Blood-claw Blue Eagle's help,

25
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:10,520
it can save us not only a lot of time

26
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,360
but also numerous troubles.

27
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,310
Everyone,

28
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,190
the eagle will fly as close

29
00:02:18,190 --> 00:02:19,870
to the ground as possible from now on.

30
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,960
So,

31
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,190
even if we're in danger,

32
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:24,960
we can make a landing.

33
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,910
Sit tight.

34
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,190
Are they the talents selected by the Xuan?

35
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,750
They look unimpressive.

36
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,470
Totally agree.

37
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:57,560
I'm Yan Huai.

38
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,190
Greetings to King of Lingwu, Mr. Chu,

39
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:01,910
Prince Wei,

40
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:03,840
and Princess Zixun.

41
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,520
General Yan Huai, don't stand on ceremony.

42
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,470
Is the place

43
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,000
all set up?

44
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:12,630
Your Highness,

45
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,150
it's all set up.

46
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:15,960
Thank you.

47
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,280
They are

48
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,680
the talents of our kingdom

49
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,630
who're qualified to enter Bloodmist Holy Land.

50
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,800
I heard some of them

51
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,080
just graduated

52
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,150
from Star Academy.

53
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,310
It should be those four.

54
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:32,840
His Majesty is so unfair.

55
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,240
Why can they enter Bloodmist Holy Land?

56
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,280
I don't know what His Majesty is thinking.

57
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:39,750
Save it.

58
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,360
Who told us not to come

59
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:42,910
from a privileged background?

60
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:46,630
Among the eight persons,

61
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:48,120
there are Prince Wei,

62
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,560
Princess Zixun, and Princess Lingshan.

63
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,710
All are members of the imperial house.

64
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,280
Apart from that,

65
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:56,080
there are Marquis Wu'an's son

66
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,680
and King of Might's grandsons.

67
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:00,680
The quota for entering Bloodmist Holy Land

68
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,680
is specially set

69
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,470
for these aristocrats.

70
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:05,960
It's better this time.

71
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,560
I heard there is a commoner.

72
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:10,400
There wasn't a single commoner in the past.

73
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,710
Shut up!

74
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,680
They are…

75
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:18,920
Your Highness,

76
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,000
they are

77
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,040
all young martial artists from various regions

78
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,000
of our kingdom.

79
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,920
As early as a month ago,

80
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,870
they were sent
to the Mount of Demonic Ancestors

81
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,000
for

82
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,270
intensive training.

83
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,600
The Competition of Five Kingdoms

84
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,190
isn't open to only those who can enter

85
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,390
Bloodmist Holy Land.

86
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,270
It's

87
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,070
a grand competition

88
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,830
for which every kingdom will send

89
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:41,070
a great many martial artists

90
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:43,480
to fight for a spot in Bloodmist Holy Land.

91
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,560
It's also

92
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,560
a competition between the kingdoms.

93
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,750
The more talents make it to the top,

94
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:50,950
the more powerful

95
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:53,040
the kingdom is.

96
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,240
They're eligible for the competition,

97
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,680
but they can't enter Bloodmist Holy Land.

98
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,630
I think

99
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,920
they must think that this is unfair.

100
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,070
There is no

101
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,310
real fairness in the world.

102
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:09,680
Making them qualified for the competition

103
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,190
is considered

104
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,800
as giving them a chance

105
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,720
to change their destiny.

106
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,920
If they can't seize it,

107
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,120
they can only blame themselves.

108
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,630
So?

109
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,240
Do you feel indignant?

110
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,510
Just now,

111
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,040
you were protesting strongly.

112
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,920
Why are you so quiet now?

113
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:40,160
Are all the talents

114
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,720
of our kingdom cowards?

115
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,270
Your Highness,

116
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,360
we are not cowards.

117
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,840
We do feel indignant.

118
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,040
Why are all the opportunities

119
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,070
given to the rich and powerful?

120
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:52,190
Can't you give us commoners a chance?

121
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:53,750
If you give us a chance,

122
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:54,830
we'll prove to you

123
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,160
we're no inferior to them.

124
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,390
Yeah, I want to challenge him!

125
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,070
Yeah, we want to challenge him too!

126
00:05:59,070 --> 00:05:59,560
That's right.

127
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,750
Ordinary people?

128
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:02,310
As far as I know,

129
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,920
most of you

130
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,000
come from different regions of the Xuan Kingdom.

131
00:06:06,630 --> 00:06:07,870
In your hometowns,

132
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,950
Even if you're not the children of officials,

133
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,000
you're by no means ordinary people.

134
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:17,160
[Practicing martial arts
requires a lot of resources.]

135
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:18,430
[They're able]

136
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:20,240
[to attain the mid
or even advanced stage of Earth level]

137
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:21,600
[in their early twenties.]

138
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,870
[Even if they're not of high status like us,]

139
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,270
[they're definitely not ordinary people.]

140
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:27,870
But

141
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,360
since you've made such a request,

142
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:33,270
I naturally can't ignore it.

143
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,070
How about this?

144
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,360
If any of you

145
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:39,160
think you can defeat them,

146
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,800
just step forward.

147
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,600
If you win,

148
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,750
I'll let you replace them

149
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:48,160
to go to Blood Spirit Pool.

150
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:49,750
What do you think?

151
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:52,660
[Zong Qiang, martial artist of the Xuan]
This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

152
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:53,940
-Yeah.
-Shall we give it a try?

153
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,190
If we can beat them,

154
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:57,160
we'll be qualified
to go to Bloodmist Holy Land.

155
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:57,600
Well…

156
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,390
Do you really mean it?

157
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,600
I'm the King of Lingwu.

158
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:03,430
I won't go back on my words.

159
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:05,920
I'm up for the challenge.

160
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:06,870
Oh no.

161
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,510
Zong Qiang got ahead of us.

162
00:07:09,190 --> 00:07:11,190
Darn it. I zoned out just now.

163
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:14,390
With Zong Qiang's
Earth-level mid-stage martial prowess,

164
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,510
securing a spot

165
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,800
is an easy task.

166
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:18,830
Tell us.

167
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,950
Who do you want to challenge?

168
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,430
Him.

169
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,190
Sure enough, it is Wang Qiming.

170
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,070
Among the four students this year,

171
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:46,510
Princess Lingshan is Lord Kang's daughter.

172
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,830
Li Qingfeng is Marquis Wu'an's son.

173
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:52,190
Qin Chen is King of Might's grandson.

174
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:55,040
Only Wang Qiming
is a man with no background.

175
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,070
He's the best person to challenge.

176
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,830
Wang Qiming,

177
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,750
go on then.

178
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:04,240
Yes.

179
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,680
Let's get started.

180
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,480
You keep saying

181
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,600
they should give ordinary people a chance.

182
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,830
But instead of challenging the powerful,

183
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:25,480
you only dare to challenge a commoner like me.

184
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,800
Is this what you call fairness?

185
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,720
Don't worry.

186
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,870
I'll go easy on you.

187
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,840
If you want to fight, just do it.

188
00:08:35,910 --> 00:08:37,440
Why talk so much nonsense?

189
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:38,670
You…

190
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:41,790
In that case,

191
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,440
take this!

192
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,550
This…

193
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:08,940
He's so strong.

194
00:09:09,460 --> 00:09:11,020
-What to do?
-He's so good.

195
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,360
Your Highness,

196
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,670
two of his ribs are broken.

197
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:24,870
That was the Saber Essence.

198
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:27,030
This man has mastered Saber Essence.

199
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,510
Saber Essence is a remarkable skill

200
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:29,840
even a Heaven-level fighter
may not master.

201
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,630
It represents the pinnacle

202
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:33,390
of a saberman's skills.

203
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,080
Well…

204
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,750
It should be the embryonic form
of Saber Essence.

205
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:40,870
But it is not far

206
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,000
from it.

207
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,150
Who else wants to challenge?

208
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:47,000
Me!

209
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,220
[Jiang Zhong, martial artist of the Xuan]

210
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,150
Who do you want to challenge?

211
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:53,790
Him.

212
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:56,720
Me?

213
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,440
This man is Qin Chen,
King of Might's grandson.

214
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,720
King of Might is the War God of the Xuan.

215
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:06,000
Does Jiang Zhong still want to win glory

216
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,240
in the army in the future?

217
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,270
There's something you don't know.

218
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,960
Qin Chen

219
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,790
was kicked out of the Qin family.

220
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:15,000
And he removed

221
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:17,320
all martial prowess of the second son
of the Qins in the year-end test.

222
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:19,080
Qin Feng, the eldest son of the Qin family,

223
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,390
challenged Qin Chen to a death battle

224
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:24,000
as soon as he came back from the border.

225
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,440
Both of them

226
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:27,000
have fallen out.

227
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,080
No wonder

228
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,320
Qin Feng and Qin Chen

229
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,870
didn't come together.

230
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:35,000
They even didn't talk to each other.

231
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:36,960
With that being said,

232
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,510
Jiang Zhong is really smart.

233
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,200
If he defeats Qin Chen,

234
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,000
he'll help Qin Feng vent his anger.

235
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:44,910
It'll be beneficial

236
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,150
to his future career.

237
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,790
Overlord Fist!

238
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:13,790
Quadruple Overlord Fist.

239
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:17,030
No wonder this fellow is so confident.

240
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,440
But…

241
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,270
How can this be?

242
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:32,700
-It's incredible.
-It only took one blow.

243
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:34,300
-How is this possible?
-How are we supposed to challenge him?

244
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:35,700
-He's too good.
-We're no match for him.

245
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,790
So powerful.

246
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,240
It seems
that the Star Academy students this year

247
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:48,390
are all exceptional fighters.

248
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,750
Who else wants to continue to challenge?

249
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,840
Even Jiang Zhong was defeated by one blow.

250
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:57,750
If we fight,

251
00:11:58,270 --> 00:11:59,200
we'll definitely lose.

252
00:12:01,270 --> 00:12:02,790
No one? Great.

253
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:07,270
You are all young talents
of the Xuan Kingdom.

254
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,630
You should think about

255
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:12,750
how to survive
the Competition of Five Kingdoms

256
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,440
instead of fighting endlessly
among ourselves.

257
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:17,510
What?

258
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,510
There are casualties

259
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:19,910
in the Competition of Five Kingdoms?

260
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,630
Of course.

261
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,160
At least one-tenth of the participants die

262
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:27,030
in the preliminary test
of the competition each year.

263
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,120
And half of them are seriously injured.

264
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:31,550
In the last competition,

265
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,670
a total of 116 young martial artists

266
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:35,600
from our kingdom entered the competition.

267
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,240
But 17 people died

268
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,200
in the preliminary test alone,

269
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:41,320
and 39 were seriously injured.

270
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:42,720
In the end,

271
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:45,440
only 19 people made it
to the arena matches.

272
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,360
Though the five kingdoms

273
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,000
are not at war with each other,

274
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:54,870
there are ongoing conflicts between us.

275
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,960
Take us and the Zhao, for example.

276
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,240
We clash with each other

277
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,630
at the border every year.

278
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,870
Thousands or even tens of thousands

279
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,910
of soldiers died because of this.

280
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,630
And

281
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,550
not only the five kingdoms

282
