319
00:16:15,550 --> 00:16:17,030
won't disappoint me.

320
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:26,310
Someone is practicing.

321
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,440
And the sound of the saber…

322
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,000
Wang Qiming?

323
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,720
If you keep practicing like this

324
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,680
for another ten years,

325
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:12,110
you may not be able
to master the real Saber Essence.

326
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:13,070
Who is it?

327
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:17,750
Qin Chen.

328
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,480
What are you doing here?

329
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,200
Besides,

330
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:23,790
