339
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,200
Nonsense.

340
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:54,310
I thought you knew something.

341
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:56,110
Now it seems that

342
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:58,510
you don't.

343
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:01,000
If there's nothing else,

344
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,110
