380
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,960
Mr. Qin,

381
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:40,750
I beg you

382
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,310
to help me.

383
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,550
I don't want to be a cripple.

384
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,240
I want to be stronger.

385
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:53,440
I want to be the number one saberman
in the five northwestern kingdoms.

386
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:06,480
Wang Qiming.

387
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:08,750
Since I know the cause of your illness,

388
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:11,160
I won't sit idly by.

389
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:14,590
Get up.

390
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:18,920
