404
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:38,510
And the numbness in the fingers is gone.

405
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:42,350
I've unclogged your blocked

406
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:43,960
and damaged meridians.

407
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,240
Two days later,

408
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,830
